The best part of growing older is getting really clear on your priorities ❤️
Thanks for the Christmas gifts @srautogroup though pretty arrogant to put your bank balance on a hoodie.

Wow.  2022 was a year I definitely won’t forget. @damonfryer & myself/team pushed the brand to the next level with a HQ in Huntington Beach, countless cars added to the fleet and not one but TWO @gumball3000’s in one year.  It’s easy to get caught up in the day to day stresses of the business but when take a minute to reflect, grateful is the only word on my mind. 

I got to build an amazing relationship with the love of my life @thecourtycourts and our amazing girls. We’ve been able to create so many special memories with B & K. I can’t wait for 2023. 

Not to mention my friends in Canada and the US. Remarkable small group of people the truly matter to me. 

And the fans, you guys literally are the only reason we get to live this life. Thank you. 

I wrote this entire post without saying a joke. That’s hard for me. 

That’s what she said.
